casebody.data:
Josephine Parkas, Appellant, v. Peter Parkas, Respondent.

Reported below, 265 App. Div. 802.

Submitted October 26, 1942; decided October 29, 1942. Frederick E. Klein for motion. David P. Siegel opposed.

Motion dismissed on the ground that the order does not finally determine the action within the meaning of the Constitution.
